#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_signs/init.lua:90
msgid "Can be written"
msgstr "Można na nim coś napisać"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_signs/init.lua:91
msgid ""
"Signs can be written and come in two variants: Wall sign and sign on a sign "
"post. Signs can be placed on the top and the sides of other blocks, but not "
"below them."
msgstr ""
"Na znakach można pisać i postawić je w dwóch wariantach: znak ścienny i znak "
"na patyku. Znaki mogą być stawiane na górze i na bokach bloków, ale nie pod "
"nimi."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_signs/init.lua:92
msgid ""
"After placing the sign, you can write something on it. You have @1 lines of "
"text with up to @2 characters for each line; anything beyond these limits is "
"lost. Not all characters are supported. The text can be changed after it's "
"written by rightclicking the sign. Can be colored and made to glow. Use bone "
"meal to remove color and glow."
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_signs/init.lua:355
msgid "Enter sign text:"
msgstr "Wpisz tekst znaku:"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_signs/init.lua:357
msgid "Maximum line length: @1"
msgstr ""

